title: GET_SUBMARINE_NUMBER_OF_AIR_LEAKS

0x093D6DDCA5B8FBAE// GetSubmarineNumberOfAirLeaks
int GET_SUBMARINE_NUMBER_OF_AIR_LEAKS(Vehicle submarine);Parameters:submarine: The submarine vehicle to check for air leaks.Returns: Returns the number of air leaks on the submarine.Checks if a Submarine has any air leaks, when there is more than 4 the player will drown.NativeDB Introduced: v2189Old name:  _GET_SUBMARINE_CRUSH_DEPTH_WARNING_STATE
